high_descs: Walk to the shelf on the left.
Pick the banana from the shelf.
Turn around and walk to the fridge at the end of the room.
Cool the banana in the fridge and take it out.
Walk to the sidetable on the right of the fridge.
Put the banana on the sidetable in front of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put the cold Banana on the SideTable.

high_descs: Walk around the white table to the wooden shelves against the wall.
Pick up the banana on the shelves.
Turn around and walk straight forward to the fridge at the wall.
Place the banana in the fridge, let it cool, then remove it.
Go to the sidetable with the microwave to the right of the fridge.
Place the banana in front of the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Cool a Banana in a fridge and place it on a SideTable.

high_descs: Turn to the left. Move to the wall. Turn to the right. Move to the wall. Turn to the left. Move to the wall. Turn to the right. Reach the shelf.
Open the refrigerator door. Place the banana on the second level. Close the door. Wait 4 seconds. Open the refrigerator door. Take the banana. Close the door.
Place the banana on the sidetable to the left on the table where the microwave is.
anns.task_desc: Find a banana, place it in the refrigerator and then on the SideTable.
